00:11:07.890 --> 00:11:11.880
- You grew up in, in a era
where, you know, globalization

00:11:11.880 --> 00:11:15.480
was an opportunity and now
people are looking more inwards.

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:19.410
- True. But you could say
that I was born into a world,

00:11:19.410 --> 00:11:23.550
the Cold War, where there
was a clear ideological split

00:11:23.550 --> 00:11:25.770
between the east and the west, you know,

00:11:25.770 --> 00:11:27.900
authoritarian regimes and freedom.

00:11:27.900 --> 00:11:31.440
And remember I started studying
in 1989 when the Berlin War

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:33.270
fell in November,

00:11:33.270 --> 00:11:35.970
and then the Soviet
Union collapsed in 1991.

00:11:35.970 --> 00:11:39.900
