00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:55.120
actually the world was not
gonna be all about green fields

00:11:55.120 --> 00:11:58.065
and, you know, rainbows and peace signs.

00:11:58.065 --> 00:12:00.250
And, and for me, of
course the, the, the sort

00:12:00.250 --> 00:12:02.560
