attack on Ukraine in 2022.

00:12:09.700 --> 00:12:12.490
And we're now starting
to see the change of a,

00:12:12.490 --> 00:12:13.745
of a world order.

00:12:13.745 --> 00:12:17.560
- But you, you say in 2008
you saw Russia change,

00:12:17.560 --> 00:12:21.790
- But let's all try to stay
calm, cool, and collected.

00:12:21.790 --> 00:12:24.520
There's a lot of this war
