00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:32.290
Thanks. Thank you. I gave a
speech right after the war.

00:12:32.290 --> 00:12:35.410
We had gotten a ceasefire
in five days where I said,

00:12:35.410 --> 00:12:37.690
you know, we should
wake up and have a look.

00:12:37.690 --> 00:12:40.720
Power politics is back,
spheres of interest is back.

00:12:40.720 --> 00:12:44.050
Russian imperialism is not
gone. So start adjusting.

00:12:44.050 --> 00:12:46.900
And of course, you know, it
wasn't a very kosher thing

00:12:46.900 --> 00:12:49.420
to say at the time, but, but,

00:12:49.420 --> 00:12:52.780
and I, I'm, I'm, you know, I'm
not happy that I was right,

00:12:52.780 --> 00:12:54.190
